<s> A publishes an ontology AO which uses a URI owned by A.....  </s>
<s> .... and B publishes another ontology BO which uses A's URI ...to do what, exactly?  </s>
<s> 1. TO say something that could not be inferred from AO alone?  </s>
<s> But that is going to happen all the time: when I order a book, I say something  </s>
